'''巴爾杜博物館槍擊案'''，是指2015年3月18日，發生於[[突尼西亞|突尼西亞]]首都[[突尼斯市|突尼斯市]]的[[槍擊|槍擊]]事件。當日12時左右，武裝份子先後攻擊了[[突尼斯議會|突尼斯議會]]，以及緊鄰的[[巴爾杜國家博物館|巴爾杜國家博物館]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Souissi|first1=Zoubeir|title=Hostage situation in Tunis as parliament, museum come under attack|url=http://rt.com/news/241873-tunisia-museum-hostage-gunfire/|accessdate=2015-03-18|work=RT TV|agency=Reuters|publisher=TV-Novosti|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110140/https://www.rt.com/news/241873-tunisia-museum-hostage-gunfire/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當地警方以處理[[恐怖攻擊|恐怖攻擊]]事件應對，击毙两名枪手<ref>{{cite news|last1=Marszal|first1=Andrew|title=Gunmen 'take hostages' in attack on Tunisia  parliament.|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/tunisia/11479898/Gunmen-take-hostages-in-attack-on-Tunisia-parliament.html|accessdate=2015-03-18|work=The Telegraph|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2015-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318130121/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/tunisia/11479898/Gunmen-take-hostages-in-attack-on-Tunisia-parliament.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方圍捕博物館內的槍手並進行攻堅成功，事後清點發現至少有19人死亡，已知其中17人是外國[[觀光客|觀光客]]<ref>{{cite news|title=突尼斯博物館遭槍手襲擊 19人喪生|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/03/150318_tunis_tourist_killing|accessdate=2015-03-18|newspaper=[[BBC中文網|BBC中文網]]|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321045641/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/03/150318_tunis_tourist_killing|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事件是突尼斯历史上死亡人数最多的恐怖袭击，超过2002年炸死21人的[[格里巴犹太教堂爆炸案|格里巴犹太教堂爆炸案]]，其中大部分亦为欧洲游客，超过30人受伤<ref name="latimes">{{cite news|title=Museum attack a 'great calamity' for Tunisia's young democracy|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-tunisia-museum-attack-20150318-story.html#page=1|accessdate=2015-03-19|work=latimes.com|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929000423/http://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-tunisia-museum-attack-20150318-story.html#page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DavidKirkpatrick"/><ref name="auto">[http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/tunisia-death-toll-in-museum-attack-rises-to-23/ar-BBiqmqN Death toll rises to 23] {{Wayback|url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/tunisia-death-toll-in-museum-attack-rises-to-23/ar-BBiqmqN |date=20180105123113 }}, msn.com; accessed 19 March 2015.</ref>。

[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]宣称对袭击事件负责，并扬言要发动更多的袭击<ref name=huff/>。两天后，该组织对也门首都[[萨那|萨那]]两座什叶派清真寺的[[2015年沙那清真寺爆炸事件|爆炸案]]表示负责，事件造成至少137人死亡<ref>{{cite news|title=Yemen crisis: Islamic State claims Sanaa mosque attacks|url=http://m.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-31989844|accessdate=2015-03-21|work=BBC News|date=2015-03-21|archive-date=2015-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150514013958/http://m.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-31989844|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
由于长期总统[[宰因·阿比丁·本·阿里|宰因·阿比丁·本·阿里]]的权力于2011年[[突尼斯革命|突尼斯革命]]被撤后，国家时常面临着伊斯兰激进分子的袭击，主要是在偏远地区。该国公民也是[[伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国|伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国]]（ISIL）的最大组成部分之一。旅游业自民主过渡以来一直是国家重要的经济命脉<ref name="DavidKirkpatrick"/>。

==袭击==
袭击当日上午，[[歌诗达迷人号|歌诗达迷人号]]和[[地中海辉煌号|地中海辉煌号]]在[[拉葛列特港|拉葛列特港]]停靠<ref>Walker, Jim. [http://www.cruiselawnews.com/2015/03/articles/terrorism-1/terrorists-kill-tourists-as-costa-fascinosa-and-msc-splendida-visit-tunis Terrorists Kill Tourists as Costa Fascinosa and MSC Splendida Visit Tunis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cruiselawnews.com/2015/03/articles/terrorism-1/terrorists-kill-tourists-as-costa-fascinosa-and-msc-splendida-visit-tunis |date=20180709112442 }}, cruiselawnews.com, 18 March 2015.</ref>。船上的一些乘客决定前往巴尔多博物馆<ref name="msc">Squires, Nick. [http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/tunisia/11479898/Tunisia-attack-tourists-taken-hostage-at-museum-near-Tunis-parliament-live.html Tunisia attack: Briton missing after shooting, says cruise company - latest] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/tunisia/11479898/Tunisia-attack-tourists-taken-hostage-at-museum-near-Tunis-parliament-live.html |date=20201128101053 }}, ''The Telegraph'', 18 March 2015.</ref>。袭击发生时，有200多名游客在附近出现<ref>[http://lainfo.es/en/2015/03/18/eight-dead-after-attack-in-tunisia-bardo-museum] {{Wayback|url=http://lainfo.es/en/2015/03/18/eight-dead-after-attack-in-tunisia-bardo-museum |date=20150402140225 }}, Eight dead after attack in Tunisia Bardo Museum], LaInfo.es, 18 March 2015.</ref>。

袭击于晚上12:30开始<ref name="DavidKirkpatrick"/>。恐怖分子乘坐公交车进入巴尔多博物馆建筑群。大量游客见状后跑进博物馆以免被枪击，袭击者追赶他们，在博物馆里把他们劫为人质<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/tunisia-parliament-attack-live-stream-militants-dead-victims-nationalities-identified-1851152|title=Tunisia Parliament Attack Live Stream: Militants Dead, Victims' Nationalities Identified, 20 Hostages In Serious Condition [PHOTOS]|date=2015-03-18|work=International Business Times|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108142559/http://www.ibtimes.com/tunisia-parliament-attack-live-stream-militants-dead-victims-nationalities-identified-1851152|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TarekAmara">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/18/us-tunisia-security-idUSKBN0ME18E20150318|title=Gunmen storm Tunisian museum, kill 17 foreign tourists|work=Reuters|date=2015-03-18|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924214524/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/18/us-tunisia-security-idUSKBN0ME18E20150318|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。围攻行为持续了三个小时，警方突入建筑击毙袭击者，一名警察和一头警犬在救援行动中身亡<ref name="TarekAmara"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/tunisia-bardo-museum-attack-hero-5359187|title=Tunisia Bardo Museum attack: Hero police dog killed in terror siege gets tearful ovation|work=Daily Mirror|date=2015-03-18|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108071913/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/tunisia-bardo-museum-attack-hero-5359187|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

突尼斯安全部队护送数十名游客远离案发现场，武装特警用枪指着临近的建筑以防万一。许多游客在恐慌中跑向安全地区，其中至少有一对夫妇带着两名儿童<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/other/attack-on-tunisian-museum-leaves-21-dead-manhunt-for-gunmen/ar-BBilNWA|title=Gunmen kill at least 20 at museum in Tunisian capital|work=msn.com|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402113230/http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/other/attack-on-tunisian-museum-leaves-21-dead-manhunt-for-gunmen/ar-BBilNWA|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

袭击期间，国会议员曾在博物馆附近的建筑{{里}}讨论为反恐立法<ref name=ahram/>，当听到枪声时，他们被迫撤离建筑。后来他们被躺在地上，给安全部队展开营救人质行动提供空间<ref name="GregBotelho">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/03/18/africa/tunisia-parliament-evacuated/|title=Tunisia museum attack kills at least 19; three suspects sought|work=CNN|date=2015-03-18|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095934/https://www.cnn.com/2015/03/18/africa/tunisia-parliament-evacuated/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==嫌疑犯==
案发第二天，[[突尼斯总理|突尼斯总理]][[哈比卜·埃西德|哈比卜·埃西德]]将亚辛·拉比底和萨伯尔·卡赫纳伊被认定为枪手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://us.cnn.com/2015/03/19/africa/tunisia-museum-attack/index.html|title=Tunisia PM: One museum attack suspect was known to security services|date=2015-03-18|work=Yahoo News|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113112302/https://us.cnn.com/2015/03/19/africa/tunisia-museum-attack/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。案发前，拉比底住在突尼斯的伊本·哈勒敦区，卡赫纳伊则住在[[卡塞林|卡塞林]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/tunisia-museum-attack-two-tunisian-born-gunmen-named-yassine-labidi-saber-khachnaoui-1492652|title=Tunisia museum attack: Two Tunisian-born gunmen named as Yassine Labidi and Saber Khachnaoui|date=2015-03-18|work=Internaional Business Times|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130163841/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/tunisia-museum-attack-two-tunisian-born-gunmen-named-yassine-labidi-saber-khachnaoui-1492652|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拉比底在[[茉莉花革命|茉莉花革命]]后因工作需要搬到[[斯法克斯|斯法克斯]]，住在那儿直至死去<ref>{{cite news|title=Although Labidi had gone to the Tunisian city of Sfax to work|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/21/africa/tunisia-museum-attack/index.html|accessdate=2015-03-19|work=CNN|date=2015-03-19|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125022747/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/21/africa/tunisia-museum-attack/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拉比底是情报部门的关注人物，皆因他和卡赫纳伊此前积极联系突尼斯的恐怖组织<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/death-toll-in-tunisia-tourist-massacre-rises-to-21-1426770597|title=Islamic State Claims Tunis Attack|work=Wall Street Journal|date=2015-03-19|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127022915/https://www.wsj.com/articles/death-toll-in-tunisia-tourist-massacre-rises-to-21-1426770597|dead-url=no}}</ref>。BBC安全记者弗兰克·加德纳表示，[[基地组织|基地组织]]的密探声称两人在利比亚[[德尔纳|德尔纳]]接受了武装分子为期两个月的培训<ref name=suspects>{{cite news|title=Tunis Bardo museum: Nine suspects arrested for links to attack|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-31960926|accessdate=2015-03-19|work=BBC News|date=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203103316/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-31960926|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

袭击第二天，警方立即展开搜捕多达三名疑似同伙的行动<ref name="guardian live updates"/>。第二天有九个人被逮捕，四个人直接与策划枪击案的基地组织有关系，五名直接与案件有关联<ref name=suspects/>。他们在袭击中所担任的角色尚未得到澄清<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/tunisia-attack-9-people-arrested-over-national-bardo-museum-raid-killed-23-1852610|title=Tunisia Attack: 9 People Arrested Over National Bardo Museum Raid That Killed 23|work=International Business Times|date=2015-03-19|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119115641/https://www.ibtimes.com/tunisia-attack-9-people-arrested-over-national-bardo-museum-raid-killed-23-1852610|dead-url=no}}</ref>
。

3月20日，突尼斯安全部长谢伊·拉菲克宣布，拉比底和卡赫纳伊此前在利比亚接受一个未定名组织的武器训练，为袭击作准备<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/03/20/africa/tunisia-museum-attack/|title=2 Tunisia museum attack suspects got weapons training in Libya, official says|author=Faith Karimi, Tim Lister and Greg Botelho, CNN|date=2015-03-20|work=CNN|accessdate=2015-03-20|archive-date=2017-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128233927/http://www.cnn.com/2015/03/20/africa/tunisia-museum-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==反应==
袭击结束时，总共十八名外国游客遇害<ref name="latimes"/><ref name=ahram/>，包括四名意大利人、一名法国人、一名俄罗斯人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.mail.ru/incident/21441746/?frommail=1|title=Жертвой теракта в Тунисе стала россиянка|work=Новости Mail.Ru|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402103641/https://news.mail.ru/incident/21441746/?frommail=1|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、一名英国侨民<ref>{{cite news|title=Briton among dead in Tunisia museum attack|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/19/briton-dead-tunisia-museum-attack-bardo|accessdate=2015-03-20|publisher=The Guardian|date=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113080812/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/19/briton-dead-tunisia-museum-attack-bardo|dead-url=no}}</ref>、两名哥伦比亚人、五名日本人、三名波兰侨民<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvn24.pl/zamach-w-tunezji-nie-zyje-trzecia-osoba-z-polski,526156,s.html|title=Zamach w Tunezji: nie żyje trzecia osoba z Polski - TVN24|work=TVN24.pl|accessdate=2015-03-20|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012073026/https://www.tvn24.pl/zamach-w-tunezji-nie-zyje-trzecia-osoba-z-polski,526156,s.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、一名澳大利亚人和一名西班牙人<ref name="lib">[http://www.liberation.fr/monde/2015/03/18/en-direct-suivez-la-situation-en-tunisie_1223143 L'attaque de Tunis, heure par heure, Libération] {{Wayback|url=http://www.liberation.fr/monde/2015/03/18/en-direct-suivez-la-situation-en-tunisie_1223143 |date=20150808093640 }}, 18 March 2015.{{fr icon}}</ref>。一名突尼斯公民、一名突尼斯警察和两名嫌犯据报身亡<ref name="latimes"/><ref name=ahram/>。超过50人受伤，其中有许多外国游客<ref name="Gunmen">{{cite web|url=http://www.news.com.au/world/africa/gunmen-in-tunisia-shoot-dead-tourists-at-national-bardo-museum/story-fnh81gzi-1227268741752|title=Gunmen in Tunisia shoot dead tourists at National Bardo Museum|work=news.com.au|date=2015-03-18|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2015-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319042122/http://www.news.com.au/world/africa/gunmen-in-tunisia-shoot-dead-tourists-at-national-bardo-museum/story-fnh81gzi-1227268741752|dead-url=no}}</ref>。经各自所在地政府的证实，有十一名波兰侨民、六名意大利人、三名日本人和七名法国侨民受伤<ref name="Gunmen"/><ref name=indy/>。地中海游轮公司报告歌诗达游轮有九名乘客被打死，十二名乘客受伤，另有六名游客至今下落不明，其中包括两名西班牙人、一名比利时人、一名英国侨民、一名法国侨民和一名日本人。邮轮公司表示，年内不会安排前往拉古莱特港的行程<ref>[http://www.msccroisieres.fr/fr_fr/A-propos-de-MSC-Croisieres/Nouvelles/Informations-Escale-Tunis.aspx Informations à propos de l'escale de Tunis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.msccroisieres.fr/fr_fr/A-propos-de-MSC-Croisieres/Nouvelles/Informations-Escale-Tunis.aspx |date=20151103164313 }}, msccroisieres, 18 March 2015. {{fr icon}}</ref>，改往马耳他<ref>{{cite news|title=Cruise ship reroutes to Malta after Tunis attack|url=http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20150321/local/cruise-ship-reroutes-to-malta-after-tunis-attack.560776|accessdate=2015-03-21|work=[[Times_of_Malta|Times of Malta]]|date=2015-03-21|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618075545/https://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20150321/local/cruise-ship-reroutes-to-malta-after-tunis-attack.560776|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

SITE情报小组分析师丽塔·卡茨（Rita Katz）表示，伊斯兰国成员在[[Twitter|Twitter]]帐号对袭击表示喜出望外，敦促突尼斯人“跟着他们的兄弟混”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/reports-shots-fired-near-major-tunisian-museum-120932301.html|title=Gunmen kill at least 20 at museum in Tunisian capital|date=2015-03-18|work=Yahoo News|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305135650/http://news.yahoo.com/reports-shots-fired-near-major-tunisian-museum-120932301.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

袭击发生第二天，伊斯兰国组织发表声明宣称为事件负责，并承诺将发动更多的袭击<ref name=huff>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/03/19/isis-tunisia-museum-attack_n_6902244.html|title=ISIS Claims Responsibility For Tunisia Museum Attack|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304210609/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/03/19/isis-tunisia-museum-attack_n_6902244.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与此同时，一个与伊斯兰国有关的[[Twitter|Twitter]]帐号公布了一名意大利籍遇害者的照片，注明其姓名弗朗西斯科·卡尔达拉（Francesco Caldara），并在上面画了个红叉，写着：“这就叫粉碎。”（It was crushed）<ref>{{cite web|title=Vittima italiana come trofeo, l'Isis: "Schiacciato il crociato"|trans_title=Italian victim as trophy, ISIS: "Crusader Crushed"|url=http://www.ilgiornale.it/news/mondo/tunisi-isis-schicciato-crociato-e-pubblica-foto-vittima-1107060.html|website=http://www.ilgiornale.it/|publisher=ilgiornale|access-date=2015-03-22|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012072849/http://www.ilgiornale.it/news/mondo/tunisi-isis-schicciato-crociato-e-pubblica-foto-vittima-1107060.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
===国内===
案发当日晚些时候，突尼斯总统[[贝吉·凯德·埃塞卜西|贝吉·凯德·埃塞卜西]]透过[[Facebook|Facebook]]宣布将发表全国讲话<ref name=ahram>{{cite news|title=UPDATE 1: 8 dead, hostages taken in Tunisia parliament, museum attack|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/125536/World/Region/BREAKING-Militants-attack-Tunisian-Parliament-Medi.aspx|accessdate=2015-03-18|agency=Agence France-Presse|publisher=Ahram|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012073320/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/125536/World/Region/BREAKING-Militants-attack-Tunisian-Parliament-Medi.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在讲话中，他表示袭击案是一场“巨大的灾难”，呼吁突尼斯民众日后谨防此类袭击<ref name="bbc.com"/>，进一步表示国家正处在“反恐战争”中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-03-19/tunisia-museum-attack-australian-among-22-killed-reports/6330786|title=Tunisia attack: Australian among 19 people, including 17 tourists, killed in attack on Bardo Museum in Tunis|work=abc.net.au|date=2015-03-18|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211013729/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-03-19/tunisia-museum-attack-australian-among-22-killed-reports/6330786|dead-url=no}}</ref>。总理哈比卜·埃西德发表声明谴责袭击，呼吁民众团结<ref name="GregBotelho"/>，还主持了内阁紧急会议<ref name=ahram/>。

袭击发生后突尼斯市区出现反恐抗议活动，据报有民众高呼：“突尼斯是自由的国家，恐怖分子滚出去<ref name="bbc.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/live/31938459|title=As it happened: Tunisia attack|work=bbc.com|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113173848/https://www.bbc.com/news/live/31938459|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”袭击当日，为安全起见，埃西德总理下令把突尼斯军队部署全国各大城市<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/19/troops-tunisia-cities-first-arrests-museum-attack-bardo|title=Tunisian troops to guard cities in aftermath of deadly museum attack|work=The Guardian|date=2015-03-19|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112234501/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/19/troops-tunisia-cities-first-arrests-museum-attack-bardo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===国际===
[[澳大利亚外交部长|澳大利亚外交部长]][[朱莉·毕晓普|朱莉·毕晓普]]称此次事件是“针对初出茅庐的民主国家的袭击”，总理[[艾伯特|艾伯特]]向袭击中遇害的澳大利亚人的家人表示亲切慰问<ref name="Gunmen"/>。[[英国外交大臣|英国外交大臣]][[菲利普·哈蒙德|菲利普·哈蒙德]]称屠杀是“懦弱的恐怖袭击”，而[[英国首相|首相]][[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]称事件是“骇人听闻野蛮行为”<ref>{{cite news|title=Tunis museum attack: Briton killed in shootings named as Sally Adey|url=http://m.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-31961338|accessdate=2015-03-20|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-03-19|archive-date=2015-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509110841/http://m.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-31961338|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[哥伦比亚总统|哥伦比亚总统]][[胡安·曼努埃尔·桑托斯|胡安·曼努埃尔·桑托斯]]对袭击中丧生的两名哥伦比亚人表示遗憾，愿意帮助他们的家人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eltiempo.com/mundo/africa/violencia-en-tunez-dejo-ocho-muertes/15418975|title=Familia de general colombiano retirado, víctima de terrorismo en Túnez|trans_title=Family of Colombian general, victims of a terrorism attack in Tunisia|publisher=ElTiempo.com|date=2015-03-18|accessdate=2015-03-18|language=es|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127224932/http://www.eltiempo.com/mundo/africa/violencia-en-tunez-dejo-ocho-muertes/15418975|dead-url=no}}</ref>，外交部亦发表声明<ref name="Gunmen"/>。法国总理[[曼纽尔·瓦尔斯|曼纽尔·瓦尔斯]]谴责此次袭击<ref name=indy>{{cite news|last1=Gander|first1=Kashmira|title=Tunisia shooting: 11 dead including two gunmen at Bardo Museum|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/shots-fired-at-tunisian-parliament-10116173.html|accessdate=2015-03-18|work=The Independent|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603121611/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/shots-fired-at-tunisian-parliament-10116173.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[意大利总理|意大利总理]][[马泰奥·伦齐|马泰奥·伦齐]]谴责此次袭击，并强调意大利是突尼斯政府的近邻<ref>{{cite news|title=Tunisia: premier Renzi condanna attacco|trans_title=Tunisia: Prime Minister Renzi condemns attack|url=http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/topnews/2015/03/18/tunisia-premier-renzi-condanna-attacco_7a138819-3fbc-46a2-be54-ffd0717be98b.html|accessdate=2015-03-18|work=Agenzia Nazionale Stampa Associata|date=2015-03-18|language=it|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012072852/http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/topnews/2015/03/18/tunisia-premier-renzi-condanna-attacco_7a138819-3fbc-46a2-be54-ffd0717be98b.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[意大利总统|总统]][[塞尔焦·马塔雷拉|塞尔焦·马塔雷拉]]谴责袭击是“史无前例的暴力实证”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2015/03/18/tunisia-mattarella-gesto-inaudita-violenza-italia-non-si-fara-intimorire/1518491/|title=Tunisi, Mattarella: "Un gesto di inaudita violenza, l'Italia non si farà intimorire" - Il Fatto Quotidiano|author=F. Q.|work=Il Fatto Quotidiano|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128163905/https://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2015/03/18/tunisia-mattarella-gesto-inaudita-violenza-italia-non-si-fara-intimorire/1518491/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。日本政府谴责袭击是“卑鄙行径”，而[[日本首相|首相]][[安倍晋三|安倍晋三]]表示东京方面正在收集更多的信息，并表示谴责<ref name="Gunmen"/>。[[西班牙外交与合作部|西班牙外交与合作部]]在一份新闻稿中谴责袭击<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lamoncloa.gob.es/serviciosdeprensa/notasprensa/maec/Paginas/2015/180315tunez.aspx|title=España condena el atentado terrorista en Túnez|trans_title=Spain condemns the terrorist attack in Tunisia|publisher=Government of Spain|date=2015-03-18|accessdate=2015-03-18|language=es|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321215419/http://www.lamoncloa.gob.es/serviciosdeprensa/notasprensa/maec/Paginas/2015/180315tunez.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

