//www.mfa.gov.sg/content/mfa/media_centre/press_room/pr/2015/201503/press_20150319.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]<ref>{{cite news|title=外交部就突尼斯巴尔杜博物馆内发生袭击事件等答问|url=http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2015-03/20/content_2836538.htm|accessdate=2015-03-22|newspaper=中央政府门户网站|date=2015-03-20|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092156/http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2015-03/20/content_2836538.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sana.sy/en/?p=32677|title=Syria strongly condemns terrorist attack against National Museum in Tunisia|publisher=SANA|date=2015-03-19|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200122112013/https://sana.sy/en/?p=32677|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[土耳其|土耳其]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.todayszaman.com/diplomacy_turkey-condemns-bardo-museum-attack-in-tunisia_375795.html|title=Turkey condemns Bardo Museum attack in Tunisia|work=Today's Zaman|date=2015-03-20|accessdate=2015-03-20|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305044351/http://www.todayszaman.com/diplomacy_turkey-condemns-bardo-museum-attack-in-tunisia_375795.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[美国|美国]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2015/03/18/statement-press-secretary-attack-tunisia-s-national-bardo-museum|title=Statement by the Press Secretary on the Attack at Tunisia’s National Bardo Museum|work=The White House|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2016-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213114211/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2015/03/18/statement-press-secretary-attack-tunisia-s-national-bardo-museum|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

